    "slug": "i-remember-my-first-meeting-with-my-management-team-when-i-became-indonesia-s-mi",
    "texto": "I remember my first meeting with my management team when I became Indonesia's Minister of Finance. I was the youngest person and the first woman ever to hold that job. Everybody else in the room was male. I knew then that I had to work harder than any man to prove to them that I was capable.",
